floodlight (0.85-0ubuntu1~ppa2) quantal; urgency=low

  * Switched logging to /var/log/floodlight with suitable logrotate
    configuration, added sensible default logging configuration.
  * Fixed up issue with simple-http jar file not being included in the
    manifest classpath correctly (actual jar name is simple.jar).
  * Added additional jython configuration to floodlight wrapper.
  * Added headers to patches.
  * Switch runtime dependency to -headless Java runtime to minimize 
    footprint.
  * Added support for setting JVM_OPTS in daemon process.

 -- James Page <james.page@ubuntu.com>  Wed, 18 Jul 2012 10:49:30 +0100

